responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "B58A9F2E45147E360A2A6D857C5DAE1C", "You could say that I see a kindred spirit in the goblins. They are as bent on destruction as we are trained to be fierce and merciless in our actions. We are both violent at the core, and yet our outward disposition is to justify our aggressions under the flag of civilization.")
